track.name: Come Rain Or Come Shine
comments: THIS IS SOME SERIOUS JAZZ LEE MORGAN ON TRUMPET JAMIE ON BASS
Come rain or shine it is always great when Art hits those drums and pulls sweet sunshine out the bag. Freddie is on top form.
This is pretty pretty at points.
IT'S HARD TO CONCENTRATE WITH THIS ASS UNDER ME BUT "THE SONG AND THE ARTIST ". SUCH A JOY AND DELIGHT  TO LISTEN TO. (PS  i CAN'T  STOP LAUGHING)
Keep moving. It oils the joint.
Art hat mich noch nie enttäuscht
Come rain or shine, this jazz lifts my spirits. Thanks Art.
I wish my four limbs were half as good as Art's left foot.
Marvellous. Art's left foot on the hi-hat is a joyful swinging thing
Love that trumpet solo!  Freddie Hubbard... RIP
